<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/771972-who-was-with-amadeo-salvatierra-in">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Who was with Amadeo Salvatierra in Venezuela? I assume it was Arturo and Ulises but they could not have been there in Jan 1976. Unless Salvatierra was being interviewed in Jan '76 and describing something that happened earlier? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
