<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">If I&apos;m not mistaken, Amadeo Salvatierra is in &quot;calle Republica de Venezuela&quot;, which is the name of a street in Mexico city. <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">If I'm not mistaken, Amadeo Salvatierra is in "calle Republica de Venezuela", which is the name of a street in Mexico city. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
