<li class='cover' id='bookCover_53413'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/53413.Hopscotch"><img alt="Hopscotch" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1367728486l/53413._SX98_.jpg" />
